      Subclasses of TileGrid in org.cell2d.space.map 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ArrayTileGrid
      An ArrayTileGrid is a type of TileGrid that stores its tile data in a rectangular two-dimensional array.
      class  HashTileGrid
      A HashTileGrid is a type of TileGrid that stores its tile data in HashMaps with grid locations as keys.
